snippet.title: Nokia N-Gage Asphalt Urban GT gameplay
snippet.description: After more than a year, I've made a new N-gage video. This time it's Asphalt Urban GT or Asphalt 1. I think this system was way too advanced for it's time, what do you think? Leave your thoughts below!
